<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Pembelian Berhasil - RAWWR REPTIL</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css"/>
  
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .success-card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 30px;
      border: none;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 50px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 90%;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .icon-circle {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      background: #198754;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 50px;
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(25, 135, 84, 0.3);
    }

    .buyer-name {
      color: #198754;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: capitalize;
    }

    .btn-back {
      background: #212529;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .btn-back:hover {
      background: #198754;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      color: white;
    }

    /* Hiasan Daun Eksotis (Floating) */
    .leaf-decor {
      position: absolute;
      opacity: 0.1;
      z-index: 1;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/892/892926.png" class="leaf-decor" style="top: 10%; left: 5%; width: 150px; transform: rotate(-20deg);">
<img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/892/892926.png" class="leaf-decor" style="bottom: 10%; right: 5%; width: 180px; transform: rotate(150deg);">

<div class="success-card animate__animated animate__zoomIn">
  <div class="icon-circle animate__animated animate__bounceIn animate__delay-1s">
    âœ“
  </div>
  
  <h1 class="fw-extrabold mb-2">RAWWR! Success!</h1>
  <p class="text-muted fs-5 mb-4">
    Selamat <span class="buyer-name"><%= buyerName %></span>, pembelian Anda telah kami terima!
  </p>

  <div class="alert alert-light border-0 py-3 mb-4" style="background: #f1f3f5; border-radius: 15px;">
    <small class="text-muted d-block">Produk sedang disiapkan:</small>
    <span class="fw-bold text-dark"><%= productName %></span>
  </div>

  <p class="small text-muted mb-4">
    Tim kami akan segera memproses pengiriman ke alamat Anda. Silakan cek email untuk detail invoice.
  </p>

  <a href="/products" class="btn-back">Kembali ke Beranda</a>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/canvas-confetti@1.6.0/dist/confetti.browser.min.js"></script>
<script>
  // Jalankan kembang api saat halaman terbuka
  var duration = 3 * 1000;
  var end = Date.now() + duration;

  (function frame() {
    confetti({
      particleCount: 3,
      angle: 60,
      spread: 55,
      origin: { x: 0 },
      colors: ['#198754', '#212529', '#ffffff']
    });
    confetti({
      particleCount: 3,
      angle: 120,
      spread: 55,
      origin: { x: 1 },
      colors: ['#198754', '#212529', '#ffffff']
    });

    if (Date.now() < end) {
      requestAnimationFrame(frame);
    }
  }());
</script>

</body>
</html>